{"id":675772,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/675772.html","date":"2022-01-14T08:26:09Z","modified":"2022-01-14T08:26:09Z","title":"【翻车现场】未来30年是中国千年来最好的30年？网民：“别侮辱北宋了”","content":"<p>北京大学国家发展研究院院长姚洋日前在“2022网易经济学家年会”上表示，2028年-2030年中国将超越美国，成为世界第一大经济体，并提到“中国未来30年是千年以来最好的30年，上一次还得回溯到北宋。因为中国又重新回到世界技术的前沿上了，我相信技术决定一切。”</p>\n<p>在网易财经发布该条新闻的微博下，引来大量网民嘲讽揶揄。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e1150c26fd8.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e1150e2b041.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e115102b5d6.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e1151251a72.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e1151454f5a.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e1151641ee5.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e115183e8f3.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e1151a3e629.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e1151c3a5c0.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e1155c7d5fc.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e1155e98f56.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e11560479ca.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e115623d827.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/01/post-675772-61e11564316b9.\" alt=\"img\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://